// Sales Portal — Storage path blocks (reference only)
//
// Canonical merged rules live in:
//   smartrefill/frontend/storage.rules
//
// Sync copies:
//   cd smartrefill/backend && npm run sync:firestore
//   cd sales-portal/backend && npm run sync:firestore
//
// Verify all copies match:
//   cd sales-portal/backend && npm run check:firestore
//
// Sales Portal sections in the canonical file:
//   - user-avatars/{userId} — read public; writes via salesPortalApi (Admin SDK)
//   - sales_portal/marketing_mats — read public; auth write (legacy client upload)
//   - Brand%20Logo — read public; curated assets
//   - payment_proofs — auth read/write (legacy client upload)
